Package src

Class Staff

java.lang.Object
src.Staff
public class Staff extends Object
Represents a staff in the restaurant. A restaurant can have many staff. A staff will be assigned to an order and reservation.

  • Constructor Details

    • Staff

      public Staff​(String EmployeeID, String Name, String Gender, int ContactNumber, String JobTitle, boolean isAvailaible)
      Creates a new staff with details. Legal process is required to sign contract with this new staff.
      Parameters:
      EmployeeID - This Staff's employee ID.
      Name - This Staff's name. Should include full name. Should not be changed after staff enrollment.
      Gender - This Staff's gender. Should not be changed after staff enrollment.
      ContactNumber - This Staff's contact number. Should not be changed after staff enrollment.
      JobTitle - This Staff's job title. Must be either waiter or manager.
      isAvailaible - This Staff's availability. Staff will always be initialized as available.
